ed="T" n="0800a15"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0800a15"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013395"><placeName>越州</placeName><placeName>稱心寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010991">大義</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0800a16"/><persName key="A010991">釋大義</persName>，字<persName key="A010991">元貞</persName>，俗姓<name>徐</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000011736"><placeName>會稽</placeName><placeName>蕭山</placeName></placeName>人也。<lb
ed="T" n="0800a17"/>以<date key="j19736021973602" when-iso="+0691-06-09"><name>天授</name>二年五月五日</date>，特稟神異，生而秀<lb
ed="T" n="0800a18"/>朗。<date key="j19756061975990" from-iso="+0696-12-03" to-iso="+0697-12-22">七歲</date>，父訓<ref type="person" target="#A010991">之</ref>以經典，日可誦數千言。<date key="j19774961977849" from-iso="+0702-02-06" to-iso="+0703-01-25">年<lb
ed="T" n="0800a19"/>十二</date>，請詣<placeName key="PL000000011596"><placeName>山陰</placeName><placeName>靈隱寺</placeName></placeName>求師，因習內法，開<lb
ed="T" n="0800a20"/>卷必通，人咸歎之。屬<persName key="A002100">中宗</persName>正位，恩制度人，<lb
ed="T" n="0800a21"/>都督<persName key="A010992">胡元禮</persName>考試經義，格中第一<ptr target="#n1257"/>。削染，配<placeName key="PL000000011707">昭<lb
ed="T" n="0800a22"/>玄寺</placeName>。自茲聽習，旁贍玄儒。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371984406" notAfter-iso="+0721-01-07"><name>開元</name>初</date>，從<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0800a23"/><persName key="A010995">圓<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>受具。復依本州<placeName key="PL000000013226">開元寺</placeName><persName key="A010996">深<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，學<lb
ed="T" n="0800a24"/>《四分律》<ptr target="#n70"/>指訓。<persName key="A010991">義</persName>因遊<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>。<persName key="A010996">深<roleName>公</roleName></persName>已亡，乃摳<lb
ed="T" n="0800a25"/>衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g517"/><placeName key="PL000000013292">法華寺</placeName><persName key="A010815">玄儼<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，其俊邁出倫。<persName key="A010815">儼</persName>云：「<anchor xml:id="begd1e25026"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e25026"/><lb
ed="T" n="0800a26"/>今傳法，非<ref type="person" target="#A010991">子</ref>而誰？」及<placeName key="PL000000013395">稱心</placeName>本寺<persName key="A010997">超<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>請<lb
ed="T" n="0800a27"/>為寺任。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>中</date>喪親，誓入<placeName key="PL000000014664"><placeName>天台</placeName><placeName>佛隴</placeName></placeName>轉藏<lb
ed="T" n="0800a28"/>經，答劬勞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g450"/>也。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>中</date>遂築北塢之室，即<persName key="A002205">支<lb
ed="T" n="0800a29"/>遁</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013355">沃<anchor xml:id="beg0800001"/>州<anchor xml:id="end0800001"/></placeName>之地也。初夢二<name>梵</name>僧曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010991">汝</ref>居此與<pb ed="T" n="0800b" xml:id="T50.2061.0800b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0800b01"/>二十日。」至<date notBefore-iso="+0762-05-17" key="j19995111999627" notAfter-iso="+0762-09-10"><name>寶應</name>初</date>，復夢曰：「本期二十日，今<lb
ed="T" n="0800b02"/>滿矣。魔賊將至，不宜更處。」無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，海賊<persName key="A010998">袁晁</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0800b03"/>竊據<placeName key="PL000000013475">剡邑</placeName>，至<anchor xml:id="beg0800sgsz1"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0800sgsz1"/><placeName key="PL000000014380"><anchor xml:id="beg0800002"/>丹<anchor xml:id="end0800002"/>丘</placeName>。<persName key="A010991">義</persName>因與<placeName key="PL000000013210">大禹寺</placeName><persName key="A010999">逈<roleName>律<lb
ed="T" n="0800b04"/>師</roleName></persName>同詣<placeName key="PL000000013557">左谿</placeName><persName key="A009605">朗<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>所，學止觀，而多精達。<lb
ed="T" n="0800b05"/>前後朝貴歸心者，相國<persName key="A008503">杜鴻漸</persName>、尚書<persName key="A011000">薛兼訓</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0800b06"/>中丞<persName key="A011001">獨孤峻</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000001670">洺州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A009438">徐嶠</persName>、次<persName key="A008847">徐浩</persName>，皆宗人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1250"/><lb
ed="T" n="0800b07"/>也。以<date from-iso="+0779-05-25" key="j20057282005756" to-iso="+0779-06-22"><name>大曆</name><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>已</sic><corr>己</corr></choice>未歲五月</date>終<anchor xml:id="begd1e25077"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e25077"/>本院，春秋八<lb
ed="T" n="0800b08"/>十九，僧臘六十<anchor xml:id="beg0800003"/>三<anchor xml:id="end0800003"/>。殯<anchor xml:id="begd1e25094"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e25094"/>寺之北塢舊居，因<lb
ed="T" n="0800b09"/>造塔焉。<persName key="A010991">義</persName>前後戒壇計二十七登，受戒弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0800b10"/>三萬餘人。終時，室中聞天樂聲，驗乎生誦<lb
ed="T" n="0800b11"/>《法華經》、《大涅槃經》小大乘戒本，以為口業德<lb
ed="T" n="0800b12"/>行，非歸<placeName key="PL000000055446">兜率</placeName>，不往淨土，未可議其生處<lb
ed="T" n="0800b13"/>也。</p>
